1
00:00:07,725 --> 00:00:11,711
♪I found a faint light
in the fading dusk♪

2
00:00:11,712 --> 00:00:15,311
♪And met your steady gaze♪

3
00:00:15,312 --> 00:00:24,132
♪One knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on♪

4
00:00:24,575 --> 00:00:27,061
♪Longing finds no place to rest♪

5
00:00:27,062 --> 00:00:29,211
♪Through drifting wind and rain♪

6
00:00:29,212 --> 00:00:32,699
♪You are the prayer within my hands♪

7
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:40,324
♪A single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows♪

8
00:00:40,325 --> 00:00:42,786
♪We made a promise long ago♪

9
00:00:42,787 --> 00:00:44,786
♪For all our days to come♪

10
00:00:44,787 --> 00:00:48,449
♪You are the fate I cannot outrun♪

11
00:00:48,450 --> 00:00:53,836
♪How much must I let go
to trade for one moment?♪

12
00:00:53,837 --> 00:00:56,457
♪Holding you close♪

13
00:00:56,637 --> 00:00:58,874
♪Would that be enough?♪

14
00:00:58,875 --> 00:00:59,459
=Echoes of Love=

15
00:00:59,460 --> 00:01:01,499
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

16
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:03,695
=Episode 15=

17
00:01:16,339 --> 00:01:18,299
Official Gu, my master

18
00:01:18,300 --> 00:01:20,132
invites you inside for a private talk.

19
00:01:37,059 --> 00:01:38,179
Miss Song,

20
00:01:38,940 --> 00:01:40,060
this way, please.

21
00:01:41,460 --> 00:01:43,978
Father, can you see me?

22
00:01:43,979 --> 00:01:45,420
Yes, I can see you.

23
00:01:45,740 --> 00:01:46,978
Can you see me?

24
00:01:46,979 --> 00:01:48,340
I can see you.

25
00:01:49,139 --> 00:01:51,099
I can see your eyes too.

26
00:01:52,139 --> 00:01:53,579
How amusing.

27
00:01:53,979 --> 00:01:56,260
Long time no see, Grand Commandant Gao.

28
00:01:57,460 --> 00:01:59,138
Be good. Go play.

29
00:01:59,139 --> 00:02:00,739
I have business to attend to.

30
00:02:09,580 --> 00:02:12,460
Indeed, nothing escapes the Young Lord.

31
00:02:13,539 --> 00:02:14,419
Very well.

32
00:02:14,420 --> 00:02:17,979
Today, we shall speak plainly

33
00:02:18,300 --> 00:02:19,939
and deal with sincerity.

34
00:02:21,580 --> 00:02:23,419
That would be best.

35
00:02:23,460 --> 00:02:24,459
However,

36
00:02:24,460 --> 00:02:26,859
Grand Commandant Gao,
you are not enough.

37
00:02:27,539 --> 00:02:30,340
Have your true master come speak to me.

38
00:02:34,339 --> 00:02:36,739
Gu Chengye,

39
00:02:36,740 --> 00:02:38,979
I truly did not misjudge you.

40
00:02:38,980 --> 00:02:41,179
But if you wish to see my master,

41
00:02:41,180 --> 00:02:43,379
you are not qualified either.

42
00:02:44,499 --> 00:02:46,859
The Beauty Portrait is in my hands.

43
00:02:47,300 --> 00:02:49,778
I could bypass the Imperial Guard

44
00:02:49,779 --> 00:02:51,620
and go straight before the throne,

45
00:02:51,860 --> 00:02:53,979
and bring charges against all of you.

46
00:02:55,140 --> 00:02:56,274
It is nothing more

47
00:02:56,275 --> 00:02:58,500
than an indecent painting.

48
00:02:59,325 --> 00:03:01,386
The only person of consequence in it

49
00:03:01,387 --> 00:03:03,379
is the Duchess.

50
00:03:03,779 --> 00:03:05,658
If you take it before the throne,

51
00:03:05,659 --> 00:03:08,179
then you, Gu Chengye,
will be destroying your own kin,

52
00:03:08,180 --> 00:03:10,378
dragging your mother's
name through disgrace,

53
00:03:10,379 --> 00:03:12,139
and sending your father, Duke Yu,

54
00:03:12,140 --> 00:03:15,180
to the imperial prison
and the execution ground.

55
00:03:19,059 --> 00:03:20,299
Young Lord,

56
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:23,220
Once you expose
even a sliver of the powers above,

57
00:03:24,539 --> 00:03:26,819
they will never let you live in peace.

58
00:03:28,140 --> 00:03:30,180
The more arrogant you are,

59
00:03:30,539 --> 00:03:33,659
the more it proves how much
the Beauty Portrait matters to you.

60
00:03:33,980 --> 00:03:35,218
That is correct.

61
00:03:35,219 --> 00:03:37,419
The Beauty Portrait is indeed important.

62
00:03:37,539 --> 00:03:39,139
But to you,

63
00:03:39,387 --> 00:03:41,068
it is useless.

64
00:03:44,260 --> 00:03:45,659
What do you mean?

65
00:03:46,499 --> 00:03:47,620
Gu Chengye.

66
00:03:48,550 --> 00:03:49,670
Go.

67
00:03:54,499 --> 00:03:55,620
You...

68
00:03:55,980 --> 00:03:58,500
Though the Beauty Portrait is important,

69
00:03:58,775 --> 00:04:00,459
without the roster of members,

70
00:04:00,460 --> 00:04:02,259
you can bring down no one.

71
00:04:02,420 --> 00:04:04,282
- Guards.
- Here.

72
00:04:06,939 --> 00:04:09,580
Refusing to hand over
the Beauty Portrait is understandable.

73
00:04:09,659 --> 00:04:11,338
But keeping her by your side

74
00:04:11,339 --> 00:04:13,338
will only bring ruin upon you.

75
00:04:13,339 --> 00:04:14,500
Young Lord,

76
00:04:14,619 --> 00:04:16,979
allow me to offer you another path.

77
00:04:17,580 --> 00:04:20,179
Kill this Miss Song,

78
00:04:20,339 --> 00:04:21,499
Then you shall

79
00:04:21,500 --> 00:04:23,978
be set among the court's nobles,

80
00:04:23,979 --> 00:04:26,780
your likeness preserved
and your name entered upon the roll.

81
00:04:35,659 --> 00:04:36,538
Young Lord,

82
00:04:36,539 --> 00:04:38,979
once your name is on the roster,

83
00:04:39,339 --> 00:04:41,659
wealth and glory will be yours.

84
00:04:42,700 --> 00:04:45,380
But if you insist on opposing me,

85
00:04:46,140 --> 00:04:48,499
the mass graves east of the city

86
00:04:48,700 --> 00:04:50,820
can spare three more feet of earth.

87
00:04:53,299 --> 00:04:54,419
Gu Chengye.

88
00:04:59,779 --> 00:05:01,379
It is said your archery

89
00:05:01,380 --> 00:05:02,979
is unmatched in the capital.

90
00:05:03,700 --> 00:05:06,140
Show us today.

91
00:05:15,580 --> 00:05:16,659
Gu Chengye,

92
00:05:17,339 --> 00:05:18,580
I do not believe

93
00:05:18,739 --> 00:05:20,419
you would truly raise your hand.

94
00:05:37,425 --> 00:05:39,549
♪Night rain falls before the courtyard♪

95
00:05:39,550 --> 00:05:44,299
♪Illuminating the partings
of the mortal world♪

96
00:05:44,300 --> 00:05:50,700
♪Strangers meet again,
the past ablaze in vivid hues♪

97
00:05:51,580 --> 00:05:55,140
♪A sharp arrow pierces through memory♪

98
00:05:55,675 --> 00:05:56,796
Gu Chengye,

99
00:05:58,099 --> 00:05:59,659
the words you once said,

100
00:06:01,099 --> 00:06:02,460
your vows,

101
00:06:04,339 --> 00:06:05,774
were they all lies?

102
00:06:05,775 --> 00:06:11,953
♪After endless sorrow endured,
love is a word too hard to sever♪

103
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:16,586
♪Past ties fade like a dream gone cold♪

104
00:06:16,587 --> 00:06:19,259
♪In giving all, we found our only joy♪

105
00:06:19,260 --> 00:06:23,186
♪That year we laughed
beneath pear blossoms♪

106
00:06:23,187 --> 00:06:24,307
I am sorry.

107
00:06:26,339 --> 00:06:28,419
You are not yet important enough

108
00:06:29,787 --> 00:06:31,746
for me to give up everything.

109
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:36,899
♪With blood upon my heart,
I bid love farewell♪

110
00:06:36,900 --> 00:06:40,979
♪No more longing will enter my dreams♪

111
00:06:40,980 --> 00:06:47,532
♪When all fades to drifting clouds,
may I share lasting peace with you♪

112
00:06:50,460 --> 00:06:51,900
I return this

113
00:06:53,539 --> 00:06:54,780
gold hairpin to you.

114
00:07:16,500 --> 00:07:20,139
♪That year we laughed
beneath pear blossoms♪

115
00:07:20,140 --> 00:07:23,714
♪One night of snow
fell wild and restless♪

116
00:07:23,715 --> 00:07:30,639
♪Every perfect ending
hides a trace of regret♪

117
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:34,139
♪With blood upon my heart,
I bid love farewell♪

118
00:07:34,140 --> 00:07:38,219
♪No more longing will enter my dreams♪

119
00:07:38,220 --> 00:07:44,538
♪When all fades to drifting clouds,
may I share lasting peace with you♪

120
00:07:44,539 --> 00:07:46,579
Good, very good.

121
00:07:46,580 --> 00:07:49,538
Young Lord, you truly understand
the greater good.

122
00:07:49,539 --> 00:07:51,140
Now,

123
00:07:51,219 --> 00:07:54,499
you are qualified
to enter the Shengtang Guild.

124
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:57,298
From this day forward, your future

125
00:07:57,299 --> 00:07:59,020
will be boundless.

126
00:08:03,487 --> 00:08:05,568
Thank you for your regard,
Grand Commandant Gao.

127
00:08:24,859 --> 00:08:26,340
Sir, the roster is gone.

128
00:08:29,460 --> 00:08:31,260
Shanguan Yu.

129
00:08:31,500 --> 00:08:32,458
Guards!

130
00:08:32,459 --> 00:08:34,019
After them, now!

131
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:49,745
(Lady Ruyi)

132
00:08:57,187 --> 00:09:00,069
It is my fault
for mishandling this matter.

133
00:09:00,459 --> 00:09:02,499
I beg Aunt to forgive me.

134
00:09:06,740 --> 00:09:08,259
My intention was

135
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:12,060
to win the Young Lord over.

136
00:09:12,299 --> 00:09:15,339
With the Commander
of the Imperial Guard protecting us,

137
00:09:15,340 --> 00:09:18,186
the Shengtang Guild
could surely help Prince Gong

138
00:09:18,187 --> 00:09:19,694
rise again.

139
00:09:20,179 --> 00:09:21,060
Enough.

140
00:09:29,179 --> 00:09:31,979
Now the Beauty Portrait and the roster

141
00:09:32,220 --> 00:09:34,499
are both in their hands.

142
00:09:35,179 --> 00:09:37,700
The labor of decades

143
00:09:37,962 --> 00:09:40,779
has been ruined by your incompetence.

144
00:09:40,980 --> 00:09:42,259
Your Highness, forgive me.

145
00:09:42,260 --> 00:09:43,779
Your Highness, forgive me.

146
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:52,859
I will intercept them at once.

147
00:09:55,179 --> 00:09:56,774
Then go.

148
00:09:56,775 --> 00:09:58,414
Yes.

149
00:10:09,687 --> 00:10:11,526
Brothel Keeper Zhou,

150
00:10:13,375 --> 00:10:14,815
I hear

151
00:10:14,980 --> 00:10:17,820
you are quite close with Shanguan Yu.

152
00:10:19,100 --> 00:10:21,578
He has served you for years.

153
00:10:21,579 --> 00:10:22,938
Do you know

154
00:10:22,939 --> 00:10:24,899
where they

155
00:10:24,980 --> 00:10:26,624
have gone?

156
00:10:26,625 --> 00:10:28,420
In reply to Your Highness,

157
00:10:28,659 --> 00:10:29,979
I

158
00:10:30,260 --> 00:10:31,619
truly do not know.

159
00:10:35,380 --> 00:10:37,099
Brothel Keeper Zhou,

160
00:10:37,860 --> 00:10:41,859
you were once the most
beautiful songstress in the capital.

161
00:10:41,860 --> 00:10:43,379
But now,

162
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:45,979
I shall have a flower

163
00:10:45,980 --> 00:10:48,300
carved upon your face,

164
00:10:49,179 --> 00:10:51,259
So you will always remember

165
00:10:51,299 --> 00:10:52,899
where you

166
00:10:53,037 --> 00:10:56,700
truly come from.

167
00:11:02,579 --> 00:11:03,739
Then

168
00:11:03,740 --> 00:11:06,259
I thank Lady Ruyi.

169
00:11:33,380 --> 00:11:34,940
Zhou Zihua,

170
00:11:35,939 --> 00:11:39,979
if the Shengtang Guild ever falters,

171
00:11:41,579 --> 00:11:44,938
you will be the first

172
00:11:44,939 --> 00:11:46,859
to bear the blame.

173
00:12:00,779 --> 00:12:02,700
Are you all right? How do you feel?

174
00:12:05,900 --> 00:12:07,139
I am fine.

175
00:12:09,860 --> 00:12:11,099
How long was I unconscious?

176
00:12:11,100 --> 00:12:13,458
Do not worry. Not long.

177
00:12:13,459 --> 00:12:15,379
He struck your false death point.

178
00:12:15,380 --> 00:12:16,859
It entered less than half an inch.

179
00:12:17,179 --> 00:12:18,340
You are not in danger.

180
00:12:19,380 --> 00:12:20,619
I know.

181
00:12:20,900 --> 00:12:22,580
Two inches above the Danzhong acupoint.

182
00:12:22,712 --> 00:12:23,912
He taught me.

183
00:12:28,779 --> 00:12:30,578
The spot you shot just now

184
00:12:30,579 --> 00:12:32,619
is two inches above the Danzhong acupoint,
a false death point.

185
00:12:32,620 --> 00:12:35,180
It can save your life
in a critical moment.

186
00:12:35,980 --> 00:12:37,099
Gu Chengye.

187
00:12:39,179 --> 00:12:40,180
I do not believe

188
00:12:40,325 --> 00:12:41,645
you would truly do it.

189
00:12:52,340 --> 00:12:53,700
You two

190
00:12:53,939 --> 00:12:56,499
prove your trust
through killing and loving.

191
00:12:58,900 --> 00:13:00,660
The price is rather high.

192
00:13:03,175 --> 00:13:04,739
If someone had to sacrifice

193
00:13:04,740 --> 00:13:06,660
to obtain the roster,

194
00:13:06,980 --> 00:13:08,060
then that arrow

195
00:13:08,179 --> 00:13:09,460
had to be mine to bear.

196
00:13:09,579 --> 00:13:11,859
If Gao Deng had entered
his name on the roster,

197
00:13:12,100 --> 00:13:14,019
he would be doomed beyond redemption.

198
00:13:14,380 --> 00:13:16,460
So I had to seize the roster.

199
00:13:17,140 --> 00:13:18,019
And that strike,

200
00:13:18,380 --> 00:13:20,019
he also had to endure.

201
00:13:22,179 --> 00:13:23,379
It is only that

202
00:13:24,740 --> 00:13:26,379
I hope he is unharmed.

203
00:13:32,050 --> 00:13:33,139
Now,

204
00:13:33,140 --> 00:13:35,778
the Beauty Portrait
and the roster are in our hands.

205
00:13:35,779 --> 00:13:37,379
Victory is within sight.

206
00:13:37,380 --> 00:13:38,660
We must not delay.

207
00:13:38,779 --> 00:13:40,739
Let us bring down
the Shengtang Guild at once.

208
00:13:41,525 --> 00:13:42,686
Zhiyun,

209
00:13:44,312 --> 00:13:45,433
I...

210
00:13:48,900 --> 00:13:50,699
There is actually

211
00:13:51,419 --> 00:13:53,099
one small regret.

212
00:14:00,179 --> 00:14:01,619
I hope you can help me.
